metadata.name: Gili T Local Legend #1
metadata.description:
This is a community-based NFT collection.  It pays tribute to the devout customers of 'Tir na nOg Irish Bar', located on the coral-fringed paradise island of Gili Trawangan, Indonesia.

Each NFT is unique and holders will receive ongoing discounts on food and drink in recognition of their loyal custom. 

There will be other benefits too, including IRL meet-ups, giveaways, access to VIP events and more. 

These benefits may change over time and the latest offerings can be found at www.tirnanogbar.com/local-legends-nft.

The total supply is fixed at 100 NFTs, and only 'legends', in whatever guise that may be, will be selected to be part of the clan.
